39
00:02:42,114 --&gt; 00:02:45,009
and &quot;Luo Yang&quot; that is in the north of Luo River.

40
00:02:45,802 --&gt; 00:02:48,764
During the late Western Zhou Dynasty and middle Spring and Autumn Period,

41
00:02:48,993 --&gt; 00:02:52,229
