42
00:02:52,746 --&gt; 00:02:59,636
For example, in the Zhou Dynasty, there was a man called &quot;Bo Yang Fu&quot; who used Yin and Yang 


43
00:02:59,858 --&gt; 00:03:01,670
to explain the phenomenon of earthquake.

44
00:03:02,082 --&gt; 00:03:08,252
and began to discuss the effect of the changes of Yin and Yang on the human body. 

45
00:03:08,766 --&gt; 00:03:12,026
