51
00:03:28,695 --&gt; 00:03:30,819
In the Spring and Autumn Period, 

52
00:03:31,056 --&gt; 00:03:35,462
Lao Tzu - founder of Taoism, said that &quot;All things leave behind them Yin, and go forward to embrace Yang, while they are harmonised by the Breath of Vacancy.&quot;

53
00:03:35,926 --&gt; 00:03:39,187
He believed that everything in the world is made of Yin and Yang

54
00:03:39,610 --&gt; 00:03:42,480
which raised the Thought of Yin and Yang to the height of philosophy.

55
00:03:43,077 --&gt; 00:03:46,454
