62
00:04:17,683 --&gt; 00:04:22,120
In State of Qi, scholars of Jixia Academy combined Yin, Yang with Five Elements

63
00:04:22,394 --&gt; 00:04:23,947
and then put forward the Five Elements Theory of Yin and Yang.

64
00:04:24,467 --&gt; 00:04:29,194
While, in the Confucianism, Yin and Yang were related to Yi.

65
00:04:29,556 --&gt; 00:04:34,271
